00:51:38,720 --> 00:51:42,880
that they've been crushed and although they've been crushed, they haven't fully

1157
00:51:42,880 --> 00:51:45,580
been squeezed. The juices haven't come out yet, although they've been crushed.

1158
00:51:54,300 --> 00:51:55,180
והכא נמי כמי שחוסרים דיכה דמי. ve'hacha nami ke'mi she'chusarim dikah dami.

1159
00:52:04,660 --> 00:52:08,040
And this case of the משנה where you have the big beam

1160
00:52:08,040 --> 00:52:11,520
on the grapes and the olives, he said to me that seems

1161
00:52:11,520 --> 00:52:14,020
