1179
00:53:02,966 --> 00:53:05,580
שמאי is only concerned with starting a process that on שבת would

1180
00:53:05,580 --> 00:53:07,560
be חילול שבת Chillul Shabbat if you were to do it. Here

1181
00:53:07,640 --> 00:53:09,220
if you were to do it, it would not be חילול שבת.

1182
00:53:08,620 --> 00:53:12,300
Chillul Shabbat. Why not? So we now see different תנאים Tannaim that

1183
00:53:12,300 --> 00:53:16,680
