00:53:44,580 --> 00:53:44,820
reason.

1195
00:53:44,940 --> 00:53:46,480
That's only if it's squeezed well.

1196
00:53:46,960 --> 00:53:49,360
Yeah, only if it's crushed well beginning ערב שבת, correct.

1197
00:53:49,460 --> 00:53:52,540
Okay, so basically our משנה then when you're putting these beams on,

1198
00:53:52,540 --> 00:53:54,620
it's because the grapes were already crushed very well.

1199
00:53:54,880 --> 00:53:55,080
Right,

1200
00:53:56,300 --> 00:53:59,040
at least well enough according to each תנא Tanna what they required.

